data.description: Act now to take advantage of this rare opportunity to own one of the most sought-after locations on Saratoga Lake with this meticulously maintained 4 BR, 3 BA home on Riley Cove. There is an impressive amount of space to entertain both inside and out beginning with an expansive family room and dining area. The open floor plan continues into the kitchen with a peninsula and huge pantry, and a first-floor bedroom with full bath. The exterior features a heated garage with finished floor, garage doors that open on both sides for ease of entertaining, spacious front deck, large private back yard with a patio,  new shed, and a dock with 14' private deeded lake rights. Conveniently located near the Saratoga Spa State Park, Saratoga Racetrack and downtown Saratoga Springs
